name: Cherrie Liu
message: Hi Team, this is Cherrie Liu, intake of NUS MBA 21 Aug. With passion in FinTech, I've recently founded a NUS MBA FinTech Club: https://www.linkedin.com/groups/13976754/. The club was created on 7 Jun, within 1 day we already have nearly 100 members in whatsapp group now. As the founder of this club, I'd like to share this great news with NUS FinTech Society and discuss how we can collaborate in the future. Cheers and look forward to hearing from you soon.
